                  <div type="textpart" subtype="face" rend="linear" n="obv" xml:lang="grc"><!--the values of the xml:lang are here: https://github.com/SigiDoc/EFES-SigiDoc/wiki/Languages-and-scripts#iana-language-and-script-subtags-->
